title: Alienware m15 R7, m17 R5, and Aurora R14 launch with AMD Ryzen CPUs
content:
Dell’s Alienware brand has launched a handful of new products, including the Alienware Aurora Ryzen Edition R14 desktop – which now comes with the new Ryzen 7 5800X3D processor – as well as the Alienware m15 R7 and m17 R5 laptops, both powered by AMD’s Ryzen 6000 series processors. The post Alienware m15 R7, m17 R5, and Aurora R14 launch with AMD Ryzen CPUs appeared first on xda-developers.
description: Alienware has announced that its latest AMD-powered gaming PCs are now available, including the Aurora R14 with a Ryzen 7 5800X3D.
